Abstract:
->Emotion detection contributes for a large domain of research. With this project I've Successfully detected and classified the assorted 
  emotions of a person based on his/her physiological signals such as body temperature, heart rate, skin resistance and pulse wave with the help of IOT sensors such as
  Galvanic Skin Resistance Sensor,Heart Rate Sensor and Body Temperature Sensor.
->The most basic emotions extracted  are relaxed, happy, angry and sad. Â 

Applications:
.Autonomous Cars
.Professional Field
.Medical Field


